metadata.title: Ecosystem Boundary
metadata.description: Data Type: Boundaries; This data layer contains the boundary of Prince William Sound-Copper River basin ecosystem, including the watershed boundary enclosing the Copper River and PWS drainages and marine areas to the edge of the continental shelf.
